dc_title_s: C-15 Geologic atlas of Pope County, Minnesota [Part A]
dc_description_s: 5 pls. Scales 1:100,000 and 1:200,000. Pl. 1, data-base map; pl. 2, bedrock geology, bedrock topography, and depth to bedrock; pl. 3, surficial geology; pl. 4, Quaternary stratigraphy; pl. 5, mineral endowment. Part B Published separately by the Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, Division of Waters. Supplementary files include ArcGis coverages, shapefiles and/or ESRI grids used to construct the plates, and metadata.
